# LangChain / LangGraph V1+ API

This project targets **LangChain ≥ 1.0** and **LangGraph ≥ 1.0**. Never suggest
APIs from older versions.

## Key package locations

| Functionality | Correct import (V1+) |
|---|---|
| Build a ReAct agent | `from langchain.agents import create_agent` |
| Chat model factory | `from langchain.chat_models import init_chat_model` |
| LangGraph in-memory saver | `from langgraph.checkpoint.memory import MemorySaver` |
| LangGraph async SQLite saver | `from langgraph.checkpoint.sqlite.aio import AsyncSqliteSaver` |
| LangGraph sync SQLite saver | `from langgraph.checkpoint.sqlite import SqliteSaver` |

Note: `AsyncSqliteSaver` lives in `langgraph.checkpoint.sqlite.aio` — this namespace
is populated by the **separate** `langgraph-checkpoint-sqlite` package which must be
declared as a dependency alongside `langgraph`.

## Common mistakes to avoid

- `create_react_agent` — pre-V1 name; use `create_agent` instead
- Assuming `langgraph.checkpoint.sqlite` is bundled — it is NOT; always declare
  `langgraph-checkpoint-sqlite>=2.0` as an explicit dependency

## Dependency declaration

```toml
"langchain>=1.0",
"langgraph>=1.0",
"langgraph-checkpoint-sqlite>=2.0",
"langchain-openai>=0.3",
```
